metadata.name: NFT NYC WALL
metadata.description:
The Walls NFT is a utility & access pass: Each NFT grants its holder access to have an NFT of their choice hand painted on a mural in a major US metro.*

The winner of this auction will be able to have their choice painted alongside the likes of TropoFarmer, King Black Bored & more for our upcoming influencer wall set to reveal June 19th in NYC

*We reserve the right to refuse painting of any NFTs that are vulgar or offensive
